<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ResepKu — Masak lebih tenang</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,600;0,9..144,800;1,9..144,300;1,9..144,600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css" />

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #FFFFFF;
      --accent-teal: #389C9A;
      --accent-yellow: #FEDB71;
      --text: #1D1D1D;
      --secondary: #F8F8F8;
      --teal-dark: #2a7876;
      --teal-light: #4db8b6;
      --muted: #888;
      --border: #e8e8e8;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ─── NAV ─── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 5vw;
      height: 72px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      transition: box-shadow 0.3s;
    }
    nav.scrolled { box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }

    .nav-brand {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
      text-decoration: none; color: var(--text);
    }
    .nav-brand-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: grid; place-items: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: transparent;
    }
    .nav-brand-icon img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .nav-brand-text strong {
      display: block; font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1;
    }
    .nav-brand-text small {
      font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none; color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .nav-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 22px; border-radius: 100px;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; border: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-ghost {
      background: transparent; color: var(--text);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--text); }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent-teal); color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--teal-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(56,156,154,0.35); }
    .btn-yellow {
      background: var(--accent-yellow); color: var(--text);
    }
    .btn-yellow:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(254,219,113,0.5); }

    /* ─── HERO ─── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 84px 5vw 56px;
      gap: 48px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 110% 50%, rgba(56,156,154,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%),
                  radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at -10% 80%, rgba(254,219,113,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-copy { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

    .hero-kicker {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(56,156,154,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(56,156,154,0.2);
      color: var(--accent-teal); border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 6px 16px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
    }
    .hero-kicker::before {
      content: ''; width: 6px; height: 6px;
      background: var(--accent-teal); border-radius: 50%;
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.4); }
    }

    .hero-heading {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
      font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
    }
    .hero-heading em {
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--accent-teal);
    }
    .hero-heading .highlight {
      position: relative; display: inline-block;
    }
    .hero-heading .highlight::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; bottom: 2px; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 8px; background: var(--accent-yellow);
      z-index: -1; border-radius: 2px;
      transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
      animation: underlineIn 0.6s 0.7s ease forwards;
    }
    @keyframes underlineIn { to { transform: scaleX(1); } }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #555;
      max-width: 500px; margin-bottom: 28px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: flex; gap: 0;
      margin-top: -4px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.4s ease both;
    }
    .hero-stat {
      padding: 0 28px 0 0;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .hero-stat:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
    .hero-stat:last-child { border-right: none; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 28px; }
    .hero-stat strong {
      display: block; font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text);
    }
    .hero-stat span { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }

    /* ─── CAROUSEL VISUAL ─── */
    .hero-visual {
      position: relative; z-index: 2;
      animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.2s ease both;
    }

    .carousel-shell {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/5;
      max-height: 580px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--secondary);
    }

    .carousel-track {
      display: flex;
      height: 100%;
      transition: transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.18, 1);
    }

    .carousel-slide {
      min-width: 100%; height: 100%;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }

    .carousel-slide img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transform: scale(1.05);
      transition: transform 8s ease;
    }
    .carousel-slide.active img { transform: scale(1); }

    .carousel-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, transparent 40%, rgba(29,29,29,0.7) 100%);
    }

    .carousel-label {
      position: absolute; bottom: 24px; left: 24px; right: 24px;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .carousel-label .meal-area {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.7; margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .carousel-label .meal-name {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600;
    }

    .carousel-dots {
      position: absolute; bottom: 24px; right: 24px;
      display: flex; gap: 6px;
    }
    .carousel-dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .carousel-dot.active {
      width: 20px; border-radius: 4px;
      background: #fff;
    }

    /* Floating badges */
    .float-badge {
      position: absolute; z-index: 10;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-radius: 16px; padding: 12px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;
      animation: floatY 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .float-badge:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: -2s; }

    @keyframes floatY {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
    }

    .float-badge-top {
      top: -20px; right: -20px;
      background: var(--accent-yellow);
    }
    .float-badge-top .badge-icon { font-size: 20px; }
    .float-badge-top .badge-text strong { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; display: block; }
    .float-badge-top .badge-text small { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(29,29,29,0.6); }

    .float-badge-bottom {
      bottom: -16px; left: -20px;
    }
    .float-badge-bottom .badge-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--accent-teal); color: #fff;
      display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 16px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .float-badge-bottom .badge-text strong { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; display: block; color: var(--text); }
    .float-badge-bottom .badge-text small { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); }

    /* Loading skeleton */
    .skeleton {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f0f0f0 25%, #e0e0e0 50%, #f0f0f0 75%);
      background-size: 200% 100%;
      animation: shimmer 1.5s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes shimmer { to { background-position: -200% 0; } }

    /* ─── FEATURES ─── */
    .section {
      padding: 76px 5vw;
    }
    .section-head {
      text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 44px;
    }
    .section-kicker {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-teal);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-head h2 {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-head p { color: #666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; }

    .features-bg { background: var(--secondary); }

    .feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: var(--bg); border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 24px 22px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: all 0.3s;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .feature-card::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .feature-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

    .feature-card:nth-child(1) .feature-icon { background: rgba(56,156,154,0.12); color: var(--accent-teal); }
    .feature-card:nth-child(2) .feature-icon { background: rgba(254,219,113,0.25); color: #d4a017; }
    .feature-card:nth-child(3) .feature-icon { background: rgba(56,156,154,0.12); color: var(--accent-teal); }
    .feature-card:nth-child(4) .feature-icon { background: rgba(254,219,113,0.25); color: #d4a017; }

    .feature-icon {
      width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 14px;
      display: grid; place-items: center;
      font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .feature-card p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #666; }

    /* ─── MEAL GRID (DISCOVERY) ─── */
    .meal-grid-section { padding: 76px 5vw 100px; }

    .meal-scroll {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .meal-card {
      border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;
      position: relative; aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      background: var(--secondary);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .meal-card:hover { transform: scale(1.02); }
    .meal-card:nth-child(2) { margin-top: 32px; }
    .meal-card:nth-child(4) { margin-top: -32px; }

    .meal-card img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.4s;
    }
    .meal-card:hover img { transform: scale(1.06); }

    .meal-card-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(29,29,29,0.85) 0%, transparent 55%);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end; padding: 20px 16px;
    }
    .meal-card-area {
      font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-yellow);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .meal-card-name {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600; color: #fff; line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .meal-card-tag {
      position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      color: #fff; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 100px; padding: 4px 10px;
    }

    /* ─── HOW IT WORKS ─── */
    .how-section { background: var(--text); padding: 100px 5vw; }
    .how-section .section-kicker { color: var(--accent-yellow); }
    .how-section .section-head h2 { color: #fff; }
    .how-section .section-head p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }

    .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 40px; }

    .step {
      padding: 36px; border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .step:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-color: rgba(56,156,154,0.4);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .step-num {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 52px; font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--accent-yellow); line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      display: block;
    }
    .step h3 {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .step p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }

    .step-divider {
      display: none; /* between steps */
    }

    /* ─── CTA BANNER ─── */
    .cta-section {
      padding: 80px 5vw;
      background: var(--accent-teal);
      text-align: center;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 80% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%),
                  radial-gradient(circle at 10% 50%, rgba(254,219,113,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
    }
    .cta-section .section-kicker { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .cta-section p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 16px;
      max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 40px; line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-white {
      background: #fff; color: var(--accent-teal);
    }
    .btn-white:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
    .btn-outline-white {
      background: transparent; color: #fff;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }
    .btn-outline-white:hover { border-color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
    footer {
      background: var(--text); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      padding: 32px 5vw; text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    footer a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: #fff; }

    /* ─── ANIMATIONS ─── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    .reveal.in-view { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
    .reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
    .reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }

    /* ─── TICKER ─── */
    .ticker-wrap {
      overflow: hidden; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 16px 0;
      background: var(--secondary);
    }
    .ticker {
      display: flex; gap: 0;
      animation: tickerMove 28s linear infinite;
    }
    @keyframes tickerMove { to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }
    .ticker-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      white-space: nowrap; padding: 0 40px;
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: #888;
    }
    .ticker-item i { color: var(--accent-teal); }

    /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding-top: 90px; }
      .hero-visual { display: none; }
      nav .nav-links { display: none; }
      .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .meal-scroll { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .meal-card:nth-child(2), .meal-card:nth-child(4) { margin-top: 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="navbar">
  <a href="/" class="nav-brand">
    <div class="nav-brand-icon"><img src="/images/7.png" alt="Logo ResepKu" /></div>
    <div class="nav-brand-text">
      <strong>ResepKu</strong>
      <small>Smart recipe planner</small>
    </div>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#features">Fitur</a></li>
    <li><a href="#discovery">Eksplorasi</a></li>
    <li><a href="#how">Cara pakai</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="nav-actions">
    <a href="/login" class="btn btn-ghost">Masuk</a>
    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Daftar gratis</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <div class="hero-kicker">Smart cooking, clear planning</div>
    <h1 class="hero-heading">
      Masak lebih <em>tenang</em>.<br>
      Rencanakan resep dengan
      <span class="highlight">satu aplikasi</span>.
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      ResepKu membantu kamu cari inspirasi resep, filter berdasarkan bahan dan region,
      simpan favorit, hitung perkiraan belanja, sampai recook history yang rapi.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i> Mulai gratis
      </a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-ghost">Masuk ke akun</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <strong>AI</strong>
        <span>Meal assistant</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <strong>∞</strong>
        <span>Filter pintar</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <strong>✦</strong>
        <span>Recook journey</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-visual">
    <div class="float-badge float-badge-top">
      <div class="badge-icon">🍳</div>
      <div class="badge-text">
        <strong>AI meal assistant</strong>
        <small>Ide masak, anytime</small>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="carousel-shell">
      <div class="carousel-track" id="carousel-track">
        <!-- slides injected by JS -->
        <div class="carousel-slide active" style="background:#e8e8e8;display:grid;place-items:center;">
          <div style="width:60px;height:60px;border-radius:50%;" class="skeleton"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-dots" id="carousel-dots"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="float-badge float-badge-bottom">
      <div class="badge-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-fire"></i></div>
      <div class="badge-text">
        <strong>Trending hari ini</strong>
        <small>Diperbarui tiap sesi</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TICKER -->
<div class="ticker-wrap">
  <div class="ticker" id="ticker">
    <!-- injected by JS -->
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="section features-bg" id="features">
  <div class="section-head reveal">
    <span class="section-kicker">Built for daily cooking</span>
    <h2>Lebih dari sekadar katalog resep.</h2>
    <p>Pengalaman dibuat agar kamu bisa langsung tahu apa yang harus dimasak, berapa estimasi belanjanya, dan bagaimana memulainya.</p>
  </div>
